{
  "stem": "15396.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and some of them were not very physically able to do it, and it was a problem getting them to-- persuading them to do it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very small groups, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a place there with a cemetery, and that was the meeting point.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then you'd go over into Spain, and then you had to come back to about 200 yards from where you had started from the-- you see, here's the French--",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Border, and the customs thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you go through, and 100 yards further down the railroad track is the Spanish border.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, they had to go around like this, and come back, and get as if they were just getting off the train, so to speak, and--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Get their stamps.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they didn't, if they were caught in Spain without that stamp, entrance stamp, they would be in big trouble, of course.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was-- I mean, you imagine then--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody in it did it somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think Beamish was the one who invented that--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That route.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then there was another man named Jonathan and Lisa Fittko who-- he had been a journalist, and he had been-- he was an expert on getting over borders because he'd been chased all over Europe by the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because some of the articles he had written which I don't think Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hitler was very pleased with.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he and his wife had rented a house down near [INAUDIBLE], and they were working there to make a living in the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think-- I think it was Beamish, or Jean [INAUDIBLE], contacted them, and what they would do is people would come there and stay with him as if they were subletting a room or something.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
